{
  "stem": "5795.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I said to them, do you-- have got anybody in the-- in the world that you could-- he said, yeah, I've got an uncle or somebody in England.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, I found out he was one of the general secretaries of the United Synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wrote.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I don't know who you are, whether you're rich or whether you're poor, whether you're religious, whether you're not, whether you do mitzvahs day after day, night after night, save this young man!",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you'll get Gan Eden in 120 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how I used to write.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I used to write.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took him over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is '45.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '47, '48, I was already in Hendon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a chuppah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who was one of the-- who was the hazzan under that chuppah?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This little fellow-- unbelievable, unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- but I believe later on he divorced his wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She divorced him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What else?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What else?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we went to-- and we lived-- we lived in Station Road, talked [NON-ENGLISH], bar mitzvahs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had, oh, a tremendous number of bar mitzvahs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The shuls would be packed, packed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a wonderful hazzan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That may be one of the reasons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in my [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] selfishness or self-opinionatedness, I hoped that, [LAUGHS] that they came to hear me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyhow, it was packed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to bring in extra chairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was a-- it was a wonderful-- it was a wonderful life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't pay very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but there you are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how it goes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, after 32 years, I retired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all my children were married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the great blow is when my eldest daughter went on Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
